## Summary

**Root cause:** Every test follows a "call it and move on" pattern — the suite is a **smoke-test masquerading as a unit-test suite**. Coverage tools report 95% because all code *paths execute*, but zero of the 10 tests verify a *business-meaningful postcondition*. 6 tests have no assertions at all; the other 4 only assert `IsNotNull`.
